This is a blog written in Python using Django web framework. I am new to Django, so this app is used to help me learn Django. It is really an excellent web framework.

Thanks very much for Mark's contribution of his blog. Please refer to:
Source code: https://github.com/mliu7/personal-django-blog
Mark's Blog: http://markliu.me

